  | AddValue (Term Value) (Term Value)
  | SubValue (Term Value) (Term Value)
  | MulValue (Term Value) (Term Value)
  | Scale (TermWrapper Rational) (Term Value)
  | ChoiceValue ChoiceId
  | SlotIntervalStart
  | SlotIntervalEnd
  | UseValue (TermWrapper ValueId)
